4f824582613f90","tid":601972,"uid":63731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"296e3401a285c71645e72b42feea3c4fba54c9af","tid":601972,"uid":17330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:18:49.000Z","msg":"berchtesgaden 重點係無咩野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打記住未天黑前搵定餐廳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"搭單問 如果係奧地利住salzburg day trip去國王湖 munich 又得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"上年有試過咁做<br />\n<br />\n如果salzburg day trip國王湖好方便，salzburg 火車站行兩步就有有巴士去國王湖<br />\n<br />\n國王湖如果你唔入內湖就半日多d, 行埋內湖就要一日<br />\n<br />\n如果要去munich, 去flix bus就ok, 兩個鐘左右既車程，平靚正<br />\n<br />\n我既行程係 munich-&gt;salzburg3日2夜，salzburg 有day pass，酒店有賣，坐巴士同去景點都包晒<br />\n<br />\nSalzburg day 1: munich 坐flix bus 去salzburg 火車站，放低行理行舊城區，上再塞<br />\nDay 2: 國王湖<br />\nDay 3: 朝早溫特山，落番山午飯再行一陣就返munich"},{"pid":"feffeee6015869006260690cafcead2449446be6","tid":601972,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"果時買邦票 包左去國王湖來回果程巴士 又包去慕尼黑程火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1dfdbc37ab8be8bad7a3843136383339ffaa3ba","tid":601972,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tripingermany.blogspot.hk/2015/06/bayern-ticket-i.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftripingermany.blogspot.hk%2F2015%2F06%2Fbayern-ticket-i.html%3Fm%3D1&d=9r6hOT1uquhmcijAzKx0j0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=24017ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tripingermany.blogspot.hk/2015/06/bayern-ticket-i.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n剛剛係隔離post介紹巴打睇邦票攻略<br />\n入面最後有詳細介紹去國王湖交通方法同用咩票最抵<br />\n參考下<br />\n<br />\n個blog另外有文章介紹慕尼黑地鐵pass etc. <br />\n非常詳細<br />\n推薦去德國既朋友睇<br />\n<br />\n交通pass真係好多 用法又複雜<br />\n